)

citFooter("If you used proj_landscape to create phylomorphospaces, cite 'phytools' (if you used the default 'BM' model) or 'mvMORPH' (if you used 'OU' or 'EB' models); use citation(\"phytools\") or citation(\"mvMORPH\"), respectively, for citation details.

If you used proj_landscape, cite 'akima'; use citation(\"akima\") for citation details.")
